JOHANNESBURG - Chad Hanekom is one of the hottest new South African fighters to be unleashed onto the international stage after a flawless amateur and pro career. Following his GKO victory last year in California, Hanekom signed for the rising promotion from Bahrain, Brave Combat Federation, for whom he will be competing in Jordan in March in their 10th exposition of Mixed Martial Arts. In this episode of The Clinch, the Sunninghill-based middleweight discusses his current and future plans. eNCA